{"tid":82223,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(港產) 十幾齣2017年值得關注既香港電影","createTime":"2017-01-15T18:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T18:13:11.000Z","uid":42848,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1762aecc34ae1e3ebd7674c2f43891c5f694b1f9","tid":82223,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T18:58:19.000Z","msg":"見無乜野做整理下今年我個人覺得睇得過既香港電影，有啲就本土題材，本土到我諗大陸都唔會比上，有啲就合拍片，馬拉大陸澳門應有盡有，但都主要係香港人做班底先擺落去，有啲就續集、大片類型，但又係夠港味先放落去，夾夾埋埋湊夠十套，希望今年多啲觀眾可以留意下港片<br />\n<br />\n《一念無明》導演：黃進<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.goldenhorse.org.tw/image/photo/2016/GHFF/285/huge/photo_3c95b9d906510c3cfa221b1e2b226e6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.goldenhorse.org.tw%2Fimage%2Fphoto%2F2016%2FGHFF%2F285%2Fhuge%2Fphoto_3c95b9d906510c3cfa221b1e2b226e6d.jpg&h=18a01df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3月上映，關注香港社會問題（精神病人、低下階層），榮鷹上年金馬最佳新導演、女配角，余文樂挑戰演技之作，曾志偉、金燕玲主演<br />\n<br />\n《失眠》 導演：邱禮濤<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.viralcham.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/114111vpggdp3r3gp84o4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.viralcham.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F114111vpggdp3r3gp84o4p.jpg&h=cc37c239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邱禮濤又再回歸cult片，黃秋生聲稱呢套係自己從影最後一部恐怖片，有關慰安婦歷史題材，早前已送檢被列為三級，不乏血腥、裸露場面<br />\n<br />\n《狂獸》導演：李子俊／《貪狼》導演：葉偉信<br />\n<img src=\"http://image11.m1905.cn/uploadfile/2016/0612/20160612014027472304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage11.m1905.cn%2Fuploadfile%2F2016%2F0612%2F20160612014027472304.jpg&h=8819fc91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.3dmgame.com/uploads/allimg/161226/305_161226201924_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.3dmgame.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F161226%2F305_161226201924_1.jpg&h=e2492e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩套似模似樣，同樣係鄭保瑞，Paco監製，都好殺破狼feel，唔同既係《狂》片動作導演係《殺破狼２》李忠志，並由新晉導演李子俊擔領，講警匪人性角力，《貪》就係洪金寶做動作設作，仲有香港電影吉祥物古天樂，延續《殺２》販賣人體器官作背景<br />\n<br />\n《春嬌救志明》導演：彭浩翔<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/s480x480/13331081_1741484669466593_1133323712314483483_n.jpg?oh=628fcac8ffd19a72ed5afddaf2b2a94a&amp;oe=5914F684\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fs480x480%2F13331081_1741484669466593_1133323712314483483_n.jpg%3Foh%3D628fcac8ffd19a72ed5afddaf2b2a94a%26oe%3D5914F684&h=a4742290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭浩翔，都係果味野，唔洗點介紹，因為我都唔知個plot，4月27日上映<br />\n<br />\n《脫皮爸爸》導演：司徒慧焯<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2016/12/22/328350/i_640x360_601448505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F328350%2Fi_640x360_601448505.jpg&h=44a1f845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同名舞台劇改編，上年東京電影節首映外加香港優先放映５場，大多評價指舞台劇過重，但衝著吳鎮宇奇幻逆緣亦值得一睇<br />\n<br />\n《風景》導演：許雅舒<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cinezen.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/20150416-%E8%AD%9A%E4%BB%A5%E8%AB%BE-%E8%A8%B1%E9%9B%85%E8%88%92_p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinezen.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F04%2F20150416-%25E8%25AD%259A%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%25AB%25BE-%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E9%259B%2585%25E8%2588%2592_p5.jpg&h=df94efc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年香港獨立電影節首映，野心頗大既傘運劇情電影，聚焦6個受2012年社會運動影響的香港人<br />\n<br />\n《拆彈專家》 導演：邱禮濤<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.yes-news.com/201606/EhmFL6UL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2F201606%2FEhmFL6UL.jpg&h=a7d80816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼寒戰、風暴、寒戰２，又一套大堆頭警匪電影，電影睇頭三隻字「炸紅隧」，多產多元既邱禮濤繼愛情夢幻號後再同劉德華合作大片，好此道者不容錯過<br />\n<br />\n《骨妹》導演：徐欣羨<br />\n<img src=\"http://aamacau.com/files/uploads/2016/12/2016-12-13_02-40-43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2Ffiles%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F2016-12-13_02-40-43.jpg&h=3f9374c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門題材香港電影，銀河映像編劇歐健兒執筆，人妻梁詠琪重回澳門舊地，回憶昔日抖骨姊妹往事，平淡中尤見情懷，2月23日上映<br />\n<br />\n《Mrs. K》導演：何宇恒 <br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/gmovie/1477194183-2580962825_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fgmovie%2F1477194183-2580962825_n.jpg&h=95797ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬拉香港合拍，惠英紅最後一套打片，跟《心魔》導演再次合作，伍伯、任達華主演，上年金馬獎最佳動作設計提名，久別江湖女打手遭逢尋仇，為保家人決定挺而走險<br />\n<br />\n《今晚打喪屍》導演：盧煒麟<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/13576000_209457446118171_2853207501503552662_o.jpg?oh=3075ccbfdfed9b0613aba270e7df7b1e&amp;oe=590C93A9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F13576000_209457446118171_2853207501503552662_o.jpg%3Foh%3D3075ccbfdfed9b0613aba270e7df7b1e%26oe%3D590C93A9&h=329c1b4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同名小說改編，事隔十幾年終於有套似樣啲既香港喪屍片，有港式武器（夾雞蛋仔機、摺鄧、路牌），演員陣容包括白只張繼聰顏卓靈，仲有萬梓良！<br />\n<br />\n《藍天白雲》 導演：張經緯<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.createhk.gov.hk/fffi/images/staffcarousel/5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.createhk.gov.hk%2Ffffi%2Fimages%2Fstaffcarousel%2F5.jpg&h=1fe51953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紀錄片導演張經緯首次嘗試劇情長片，現實社會題材，女警女學生犯人惺惺相惜，猶似女版《踏血尋梅》<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，今年仲有火火既《女士復仇》(故仔有啲似the other woman)，馮志強既《大樂師為愛配樂》、彭秀慧既《29+1》、Tonick恆仔既《救僵清道夫》<br />\n仲有啲戲係香港導演但主要係中台演員同製作班底，例如許鞍華既《明月幾時有》，徐克既《西遊伏妖篇》、郭子健既《悟空傳》、袁和平既《奇門遁甲》我都認為係值得留意下，但避重就輕就無放落去"},{"pid":"c83b29dab052e1e7983180925775249dbbdf72a2","tid":82223,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:03:39.000Z","msg":"等左藍天白雲勁耐都未上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97bc2e37b9df2441dec89e229dbb028752b2f41","tid":82223,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:07:11.000Z","msg":"上面果堆都只係值得留意下,以下係我個人認為係必睇既電影<br />\n捉妖記2、我要發達、鐵道飛虎、功夫瑜咖、決戰食神、劉偉強執導既建軍大業、喵星人、三國殺幻、追龍"},{"pid":"7ddc598d8e97befd2ed2a34dda27ff4d2f97a1a0","tid":82223,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor